					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The logic to handle the DS cart edge protocol is probably more complex than the logic to handle the SD protocol. So the best bet is to take the microSD out of your R4 and put it in a Super EverDrive, SuperCard, or something else that accepts SD or microSD.</div>

